x;">Last week, I shared a
<a href=3D"https://email.puck.news/e/c/eyJlbWFpbF9pZCI6ImRnVDJ4Z1lEQUt2Uktx=
clJLZ0dVN0pEcEdJaUZ1ZXVpUGhxdGZDND0iLCJocmVmIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly9wdWNrLm5ld3Mvd2F=
